data.description: LOOK NO FURTHER! Great twin home in Prospect Park located on a beautiful block! Offers living room, dining room with sliding doors to large covered rear deck overlooking the fenced in rear yard. A gallery  kitchen with oak cabinets and granite countertops completes the first floor. Second floor has 3 bedrooms and one bathroom. Full finished basement with large family room and an additional fully updated bathroom. HUD owned property sold AS IS. FHA Case #441-890737. Property qualifies for FHA insured financing, pending FHA appraisal. Home is sold as is, seller makes no representations regarding the condition of the property. Buyer is responsible for ALL transfer taxes, U&O, tax certs and for turning utilities on and off for inspections. Buyer's agent MUST be present for all showings. Schedule your appointment today and remember - THE HIGHEST BID WINS!!!!!!!!!!!!
